dct_title_s: Il vero ritratto de Cales, preso a Inglesi del re cristianissimo l'an MDLVIII
dct_description_sm: View of siege of Calais (Chales), shows town, attack and surrounding area including camps, sea, title in box at lower right, with key which is continued in box at lower left, with Duchetti's name and Orlandi, the latter clearly added.
Small portion of English coast showing Dover at top.
